metadata.name: Eccentric Petals of Love
metadata.description:
Is it weird
That I feel flowers
When we touch?

Is it weird
That I bloom
When you hold me tight? 

Is it weird
That my eyes light up
When I close them?

Is it weird
That I taste light
When we kiss? 

I guess it is weird
But it's just with you
Everything feels right
But weird
But right

-----

Art created by Nadhsan on 8th January 2020
